Feature: To validate the saucedemo login page

  Scenario Outline: To validate the login functionality with valid credentials
    Given The user has to be in saucrdemo login page
    When The user has to fill username and pasword
    And The user click the login button
    Then The user in invalid login page

    Examples: 
      | username                | pasword      |
      | standard_user           | secret_sauce |
      | locked_out_user         | secret_sauce |
      | problem_user            | secret_sauce |
      | performance_glitch_user | secret_sauce |
